, 19 Nov 2024 05:27:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/iran-israel-among-rivals-showcase-their-arms-vietnam-defence-expo-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>英国《金融时报》报道，欧盟要求中国企业进行技术转让</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-demand-tech-transfers-chinese-companies-ft-reports-2024-11-19/</link><description>英国《金融时报》周二援引两位欧盟高级官员的话报道称，欧盟正计划迫使中国企业向欧洲企业转让技术，以换取欧盟补贴。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 05:13:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-demand-tech-transfers-chinese-companies-ft-reports-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>G20领导人在里约峰会最后一天将焦点转向气候变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/g20-leaders-turn-focus-climate-change-rio-summits-last-day-2024-11-19/</link><description>领导人开会讨论可持续发展和向清洁能源过渡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 05:06:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/g20-leaders-turn-focus-climate-change-rio-summits-last-day-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯和中国外长在G20会议期间讨论关系、乌克兰和朝鲜半岛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-chinese-foreign-ministers-discuss-ties-ukraine-korean-peninsula-g20-2024-11-19/</link><description>两国外交部周二表示，中国和俄罗斯外长在巴西二十国集团会议期间讨论了双边关系、乌克兰冲突和朝鲜半岛局势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 04:50:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-chinese-foreign-ministers-discuss-ties-ukraine-korean-peninsula-g20-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>“香港47”：对民主人士入狱的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-47-reaction-jailings-democrats-landmark-national-security-trial-2024-11-19/</link><description>批评人士称，这是对金融中心法治的重大打击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 03:56:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-47-reaction-jailings-democrats-landmark-national-security-trial-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国外长会见印度外长呼吁恢复直航</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-foreign-minister-meets-indian-counterpart-calls-resumption-direct-flights-2024-11-19/</link><description>中国外交部周二发表声明称，中国外交部长王毅周一在里约热内卢会见了印度外长苏杰生，并呼吁恢复两国之间的直航。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 03:25:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-foreign-minister-meets-indian-counterpart-calls-resumption-direct-flights-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>股市走高，美元暂停，市场等待特朗普任命</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-19/</link><description>周二，全球股市指数上涨 1%，而美国债券收益率和美元则从数月高位回落，交易员等待当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的内阁选择，并试图评估美国利率前景。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 02:40:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院判处民主活动人士戴耀廷10年监禁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-sentences-pro-democracy-activist-benny-tai-10-years-prison-2024-11-19/</link><description>香港高等法院周二在长达数年的国家安全审判中判处一名主要民主活动人士入狱十年，该审判损害了香港一度活跃的民主运动，并引起了全球批评。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 02:38:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-sentences-pro-democracy-activist-benny-tai-10-years-prison-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>由于最近的袭击事件导致神经紧张，中国小学发生车祸，学生受伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/multiple-students-injured-outside-primary-school-chinas-changde-says-state-media-2024-11-19/</link><description>湖南省常德市一所小学外，一辆SUV撞人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 02:31:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/multiple-students-injured-outside-primary-school-chinas-changde-says-state-media-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>条款清单显示，阿里巴巴公布了 50 亿美元双币债券的初步价格指导</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/alibaba-delivers-initial-price-guidance-5-billion-dual-currency-bond-term-sheet-2024-11-19/</link><description>根据路透社周二审阅的一份条款清单，阿里巴巴集团已向投资者提供了其 50 亿美元双币债券的初步价格指导。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 01:04:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/alibaba-delivers-initial-price-guidance-5-billion-dual-currency-bond-term-sheet-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>45名香港民主人士在具有里程碑意义的审判中被监禁招致批评</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hundreds-queue-sentencing-47-hong-kong-democrats-2024-11-19/</link><description>被认定为“组织者”的前法律学者戴耀廷被判处 10 年监禁，这是 2020 年国家安全法迄今为止最长的刑期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 01:01:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hundreds-queue-sentencing-47-hong-kong-democrats-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国快递集团顺丰控股将在香港上市筹集至多7.927亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sf-holding-raise-7927-mln-its-hk-ipo-2024-11-18/</link><description>中国最大的快递公司顺丰控股周二表示，计划在香港上市筹集至多61.7亿港元（合7.9271亿美元），这是香港资本市场复苏的最新迹象。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 22:22:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sf-holding-raise-7927-mln-its-hk-ipo-2024-11-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>